	<div id="main">
					<div class="post-128330 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-agriculture-food category-policy-government tag-california tag-farming tag-food-manufacturers tag-food-transparency tag-gmos tag-prop-37 tag-proposition-37 tag-transparency" id="post-128330">



